## Data Schema

- `chrom`: Chromosome
- `pos`: Position
- `ref`: Reference allele
- `alt`: Alternate allele
- `AC`: Allele count
- `AN`: Allele number
- `AF`: Allele frequency
- `MAF`: Minor allele frequency
- `consequence`: Consequence type (after grouping)
- `original_consequence`: Original Ensembl VEP consequence (before grouping)
